data.description: Your chance to live in a custom-built, corner-lot home. Beautiful low-maintenance landscaping with an unobstructed bay view deck. Open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, elegant interior, gourmet kitchen, high-end features & appliances, porcelain plank floors, softened corners throughout. Custom cabinets, sconces and lighting, no details overlooked. Embrace tranquility & modern coastal living in this one-of-a-kind home. Located in one of the best & most convenient Bay Park neighborhoods.
